text: Tyler: "Hey, I'm Tyler Posey aka Scott McCall and tonight I wanted to do something a little bit
different and special to honor my friend Crystal Reed aka Allison Argent. I put together a
list of things that I've learned about her over the years that may surprise you, the
fans. Here are the top 10 things you did not know about Allison Argent. Number 10 - Instead
of horse hair, Allison's strings for her bow with the last remaining hair of the unicorn.
Pff what? Number nine - Allison doesn't have followers on Twitter, she has fanatics. Number
eight - when Allison goes to the airport security, the TSA agents take off their shoes and their
shirts. Number seven - Swag is Justin Bieber's nickname for Allison, that's why he says it
so much. Number six - When allison texts lol on the phone, the phone literally laughs out
loud. Number five - Allison doesn't own an umbrella, rain knows better than to fall on
her head. Number four - Allison has only placed the bottle only once in her entire life and
that bottle is still spinning. Number three - Allison was the true inspiration for Taylor
Swift's I Knew You Were Trouble. Number two - When Allison talks, Kanye actually lets
her finish. The number one you don't know about Allison Argent: Allison is beautiful
and courageous and smart and talented and funny and overall an incredible person, but
you probably already knew that. So let's give it up for Crystal Reed everybody."
